classDiagram
    %% PawPal+ final class diagram — matches pawpal_system.py after Phase 4/5.

    class Owner {
        +str name
        +int minutes_available
        +list~str~ preferences
        +list~Pet~ pets
        +add_pet(pet: Pet) None
        +list_pets() list~Pet~
        +all_tasks() list~Pet,Task~
    }

    class Pet {
        +str name
        +str species
        +str breed
        +list~Task~ tasks
        +add_task(task: Task) None
        +remove_task(task: Task) None
    }

    class Task {
        +str name
        +int duration_min
        +str priority
        +str frequency
        +str time
        +date due_date
        +bool done
        +mark_complete() None
        +priority_value() int
        +next_occurrence() Task
    }

    class Scheduler {
        +Owner owner
        +sort_by_time(tasks) list~Task~
        +filter_tasks(pet_name, done) list~Task~
        +complete_task(pet, task) Task
        +detect_conflicts() list~str~
        +build_plan() list~Pet,Task~
        +explain() str
    }

    Owner "1" --> "*" Pet : has
    Pet "1" --> "*" Task : has
    Scheduler --> Owner : plans for
    Scheduler ..> Task : sorts / filters / detects conflicts
    Task ..> Task : next_occurrence creates
